Type `usage` to list command line arguments.
> Usage: symta [OPTION] <SRC_DIR> [DST_DIR]
       symta [OPTION] <SRC_DIR/main.s> [DST_DIR]
Produce DST_DIR/sbc and DST_DIR/run from SRC_DIR/src
If DST_DIR is unspecified, SRC_DIR is used instead

OPTIONS:
       -r <root_dir>   search root_dir for compiler files
       -v              print version
       -h              print this help
       -e <expr>       evaluates expression
       -f <file>       evaluates a file
> 
